LEAH: Hey!

31:51.917 --> 31:53.667
Hey, Erin.

31:54.375 --> 31:55.750
I thought that was you.

31:57.291 --> 31:58.500
How have you been?

31:59.625 --> 32:00.542
I'm okay.

32:00.625 --> 32:01.917
Well, look, I know
that it's a Sunday,

32:02.000 --> 32:05.834
but, uh, Daniel's throwing
a party tonight.

32:05.917 --> 32:10.542
I told Beau, but he said
that you guys weren't
really, like, talking.

32:10.625 --> 32:12.834
You're talking to Beau now?

32:12.917 --> 32:14.458
What happened with you guys?

32:14.542 --> 32:16.834
It's nothing.
We're just on a hiatus.

32:16.917 --> 32:18.333
You should come.

32:18.417 --> 32:20.667
It'll be, like,
so good for you.

32:20.750 --> 32:23.375
I was thinking of
reorganizing my closet.

32:23.458 --> 32:25.792
-There's this video
I saw online...
-LEAH: Fuck!

32:25.875 --> 32:27.583
Oh, my God. Okay.

32:28.917 --> 32:30.917
God, it's everywhere now.
(CHUCKLES)

32:31.750 --> 32:32.917
Life is hard.

32:34.375 --> 32:36.875
I gotta go, uh,
but you should come.

32:37.542 --> 32:39.792
Yeah. I'll try to make it.

32:40.291 --> 32:41.542
LEAH: Peace!

32:42.500 --> 32:44.625
(MUSIC PLAYING)

33:49.500 --> 33:51.291
(MUSIC CONTINUES)

33:59.917 --> 34:01.458
BEAU: Stealing alcohol?

34:02.834 --> 34:04.166
-You scared me.
-Can I ask you something?

34:06.834 --> 34:08.625
Without you getting offended.

34:10.708 --> 34:12.041
ERIN: Okay.

34:12.125 --> 34:14.250
How are you holding up?

34:14.333 --> 34:16.250
You're looking
a little frayed.

34:17.750 --> 34:18.958
I'm fine.

34:19.041 --> 34:20.667
BEAU: Just asking
just to make sure
that you're okay.

34:20.750 --> 34:21.291
Breakups can be difficult.

34:22.708 --> 34:23.625
(LAUGHS)

34:23.708 --> 34:25.500
-BEAU: What?
-(CHUCKLES)

34:25.583 --> 34:26.667
You know,

34:26.750 --> 34:30.625
I actually thought you were
gonna say something nice.

34:30.708 --> 34:32.208
Maybe you were going
to act like a human.

34:32.291 --> 34:35.583
But now what?
You're fucking Leah.

34:35.667 --> 34:37.458
BEAU: Leah's just a friend.

34:37.542 --> 34:38.750
You know what?

34:38.833 --> 34:42.166
I'm seeing someone too now.
It'd be rude not to tell you.

34:42.250 --> 34:44.041
He's a writer. Semi-famous.

34:44.125 --> 34:47.083
He's been called
"the voice of his generation."

34:51.333 --> 34:53.125
I don't want
to do this with you.

34:53.833 --> 34:55.041
(SIGHS)

34:56.291 --> 34:57.375
You know,

34:58.041 --> 35:00.500
I'm making my own movie now.

35:00.583 --> 35:02.000
It's a documentary.

35:02.458 --> 35:03.375
BEAU: About what?

35:03.458 --> 35:05.500
My burgeoning
new relationship.

35:05.583 --> 35:09.041
BEAU: (SCOFFS) Your burgeoning
new relationship?

35:09.125 --> 35:10.583
Yeah.

35:10.667 --> 35:12.583
Can I just give you a hug?

35:14.041 --> 35:16.375
Only if it's a platonic hug.

35:36.709 --> 35:37.792
Wait.

35:47.333 --> 35:48.959
PAUL: You saw Beau yesterday?

35:49.875 --> 35:50.291
(EXHALES) Yeah.

35:55.959 --> 35:57.917
He, um...

35:58.000 --> 36:00.792
He told me that
he wanted to hang out again,

36:01.959 --> 36:04.000
but I said
I was doing other things.

36:08.458 --> 36:10.583
Do you think
you'll talk to him again?

36:14.583 --> 36:16.041
Probably not.

36:20.583 --> 36:22.000
I have a surprise for you.

36:23.333 --> 36:25.208
-Really?
-Yeah.

36:28.333 --> 36:30.041
It's MDMA. (CHUCKLES)

36:30.834 --> 36:33.250
You bought me ecstasy?

36:34.375 --> 36:38.250
My mom keeps sending me these
panicked emails about

36:38.333 --> 36:43.125
all the drugs she thinks
I'm taking because
of stuff I posted online.

36:43.208 --> 36:47.458
"I don't understand why
you must reject me with
your terrible behavior.

36:49.000 --> 36:52.834
"When I send you an email
I would like you
to respond to it.

36:52.917 --> 36:55.625
"Your father may continue to
unblinkingly support you,

36:55.709 --> 36:58.166
"but I see what you post
on your web feeds.

36:59.291 --> 37:01.500
"Actions speak louder
than words.

37:02.834 --> 37:06.250
"It doesn't matter to you
whether you have
a mother or not."

37:06.333 --> 37:09.500
-Do you feel bad
reading that...
-While I'm on drugs?

37:12.667 --> 37:14.917
No. No, I just feel like

37:16.208 --> 37:17.709
she's ruining the drugs.

37:17.792 --> 37:21.500
My dad used to,
like, smoke weed

37:21.583 --> 37:24.583
and make me smoke weed
with him every night.

37:24.667 --> 37:26.291
I used to really sad about it

37:26.375 --> 37:28.458
but he'd just get mad
if he didn't smoke.

37:30.834 --> 37:32.125
Yeah.

37:32.208 --> 37:36.125
I don't want her
to feel like she's
failed as a parent,

37:36.208 --> 37:38.959
but I don't really
want to respond
to her emails either.

37:40.041 --> 37:42.500
We used to have these
crazy screaming fights.

37:42.583 --> 37:43.667
What about?

37:43.750 --> 37:47.083
When I was in high school,
I used to think the only

37:48.250 --> 37:51.208
solution to the anxiety
I was feeling all the time

37:51.291 --> 37:54.417
would be for me... For her

37:54.500 --> 37:57.333
to create all these
rules and punishments

37:57.417 --> 37:58.500
that went way beyond
reasonable.

38:00.750 --> 38:01.500
To take my control away.

38:04.792 --> 38:05.417
She didn't get it. She...

38:09.750 --> 38:12.583
I wanted to punish her back
for not understanding me.

38:13.625 --> 38:16.083
You know, they moved here
so I could become a...

38:16.917 --> 38:19.417
A doctor or a lawyer.

38:19.500 --> 38:23.750
Or something else
immigrants want their
American kids to be,

38:25.542 --> 38:27.792
but then I told them
I wanted to be a writer.

38:29.959 --> 38:32.208
You know, when I was
in college, they...

38:33.208 --> 38:35.041
They gave up
and went back to Taiwan.

38:35.125 --> 38:38.417
You don't think they went
back to Taiwan
because of you, do you?

38:38.500 --> 38:40.917
It was part of it. Yeah.

38:43.083 --> 38:44.333
After that period,

38:44.417 --> 38:47.375
I decided it was just easier
for me to be emotionless.

38:48.709 --> 38:50.375
More like I was
when I was a kid.

38:51.375 --> 38:52.583
ERIN: How much more?

38:54.083 --> 38:55.166
A lot.

38:57.333 --> 38:59.083
PAUL: Can I read you
something I wrote?

38:59.166 --> 39:01.250
"They walked arm in arm
down the street.

39:01.333 --> 39:06.083
"Reality had taken on the look
of a children's storybook.

39:06.166 --> 39:10.709
"Joanna asked Alex
if he'd ever been in love.

39:11.750 --> 39:14.834
"Alex thought about it
for a moment.

39:16.000 --> 39:19.500
"A light blinked on and off
in the sky.

39:19.583 --> 39:24.417
"He imagined being taken up
to the UFO

39:24.500 --> 39:27.291
"and bathed
in the radiant glow

39:27.375 --> 39:32.417
"of a many-tentacled synthetic
examination probe.

39:32.500 --> 39:34.333
"Maybe that was
what love felt like."

39:37.834 --> 39:39.792
I wanna go somewhere with you.

39:39.875 --> 39:42.667
-We could fly somewhere.
-We could go to Niagara Falls.

39:42.750 --> 39:46.709
If I go to Niagara,
I would peak on ecstasy

39:46.792 --> 39:48.625
in a one size
too large rain slicker

39:48.709 --> 39:50.208
while the boat takes you
under the water.

39:50.291 --> 39:51.709
That's too cliched.

39:51.792 --> 39:55.125
I would sit
at a high stakes poker table

39:55.208 --> 39:59.208
in an Indian casino wearing
sunglasses and a baseball cap,

39:59.291 --> 40:01.667
-smoke a cigarette...
-Better...

40:01.750 --> 40:05.333
Then say,
"Too rich for my blood, baby."

40:05.417 --> 40:08.125
We could get married
at one of the stupid chapels.

40:08.208 --> 40:10.458
There's a lot of ions
in the water.

40:10.542 --> 40:12.917
(EXHALES)
So it's really romantic.

40:13.583 --> 40:15.291
(JINGLE BELLS  PLAYING)

40:30.709 --> 40:32.208
(LAUGHING)

40:35.917 --> 40:39.917
PAUL: Ah, this is what
the universe created,
after whatever billion years.

40:44.291 --> 40:44.667
How do you feel?

40:46.667 --> 40:49.834
-A little depleted.
-What?

40:51.667 --> 40:52.917
Kinda tired.

40:53.000 --> 40:55.875
You should not have even
started feeling it yet.

40:55.959 --> 40:58.917
-What?
-Wait, we only took the MDMA,
like, 20 minutes ago.

40:59.000 --> 41:00.166
(CHUCKLES)

41:01.125 --> 41:03.542
Mmm, I forgot. (CHUCKLES)

41:03.625 --> 41:03.709
Oh.

41:05.834 --> 41:08.000
I thought maybe the drugs
were fake.

41:08.083 --> 41:09.250
(EXHALES)

41:41.291 --> 41:45.458
You see, when God is working,
a prophet is not a preacher.

41:45.542 --> 41:46.542
They speak from
the mouth of God.

41:46.625 --> 41:49.750
and He said, "How you will
know my prophets?"

41:49.834 --> 41:52.875
He said, "You will know them
by their works."

41:52.959 --> 41:57.250
So, I have to show you
the proof that his here
is made by God himself.

41:57.333 --> 42:02.458
You see, when God is
using you, it's different
from you in your normal body.

42:02.542 --> 42:05.166
He take you out of you
and He control your mind.

42:05.250 --> 42:07.208
And He control your thinking.

42:07.291 --> 42:10.458
