talking to you
from the heaven.

42:10.542 --> 42:11.959
Praise the Lord.

42:12.041 --> 42:14.208
And this symbol here
represents the sun.

42:14.834 --> 42:16.583
This one right here.

42:16.667 --> 42:19.250
Everywhere
you go in the world,
you see the same sun.

42:19.750 --> 42:20.917
Hallelujah.

42:23.709 --> 42:25.083
(INAUDIBLE)

