for you. Jose!

43:37.583 --> 43:41.834
His fee is $50.
You may film Jose.

43:41.917 --> 43:43.250
-Jose's often filmed
for a lot of ceremonies.
-Say hi.

43:43.333 --> 43:45.291
PAUL: Oh, good. That's good.

43:45.375 --> 43:47.667
MARSHA: And don't forget
to tip your witness.

43:47.750 --> 43:49.875
REVEREND ELVIS:
Come on, it's time to go.

43:49.959 --> 43:51.625
Hi, come on. Let's go.

43:51.709 --> 43:53.583
We're gonna get you
married now.

43:53.667 --> 43:56.667
Here we go, honey.
There's Paul right there
waiting for you.

43:56.750 --> 43:58.709
Paul, how are you?

43:58.792 --> 43:59.625
-I believe
you know this girl.
-What?

43:59.709 --> 44:03.041
All right, I want you
to get up there.

44:03.125 --> 44:04.917
Great, great.

44:05.000 --> 44:07.250
Well, guys, here we are
in beautiful Niagara Falls,

44:07.333 --> 44:09.625
ready to join you two
in beautiful marriage.

44:09.709 --> 44:13.291
Now, marriage is
a beautiful bond that
grows and grows and grows.

44:13.375 --> 44:15.041
And as you grow, you share.

44:15.125 --> 44:16.875
You share your lives together.

44:16.959 --> 44:19.625
You share times together.
